title: "gaoshanwen-skill: An AI Agent SKILL Simulating Macroeconomist Gao Shanwen's Analytical Framework and Expression Style"
abstract: "This SKILL preserves and transmits the analytical framework and expression style of Mr. Gao Shanwen (1971-2026), one of the most influential macroeconomists in China's capital markets. It includes five core analytical frameworks (Asset Revaluation Theory, Capacity Cycle, Inventory Cycle, Hog Cycle Inflation Analysis, Real Estate Three-Stage Adjustment), 7 reference documents, 10 worked examples, and 4 SKILL variants. Cross-platform compatible with OpenClaw, Hermes, Claude Code, Trae, Codex, Cursor, and Mavis agents. Designed for educational, research, and content creation purposes. All outputs are AI-simulated and do not represent Mr. Gao Shanwen's actual views."
